  "text": "Although the BD condition realizes the lUI free channel, perfect nulling is too strict. To ease the required condition, we have proposed partial nulling in a single stream transmis sion [CITATION_1] . Here, the partial nulling is extended to multi-stream transmission as a generalized approach to BD.",
